
= enumerate_words

  Rails plugin for enumerating words in a view.

== Description

  This is a gem plugin for Ruby on Rails applications to enumerate some words
  ina view.

== Installation

=== Archive Installation

	rake install

=== Gem Installation

	gem install enumerate_words


== Features/Problems


== Synopsis

  <% enumerate_words do |_and_| %>
    Dog <%=_and_%> Cat <%=_and_%> Rat
    <%# => Dog, Cat and Rat %>
  <% end %>

